#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Attributes/SeoMeta.php:168
msgid "Analyzes keyword usage and positioning within meta descriptions to ensure relevance without oversaturation."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Attributes/SeoMeta.php:169
msgid "Checks if meta descriptions fall within the optimal character range to avoid truncation in search results. Provides recommendations when descriptions are too short or lengthy, helping maximize snippet visibility and engagement."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Attributes/SeoMeta.php:170
msgid "Evaluates meta title length and quality, ensuring optimal character count and structure for search engine visibility."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Attributes/SeoMeta.php:171
msgid "Evaluates primary and secondary keyword placement in meta titles, prioritizing optimal positioning for maximum search visibility."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Attributes/SeoMeta.php:172
msgid "Validates meta title length to ensure optimal display in search results without truncation while containing sufficient information."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Attributes/SeoMeta.php:173
msgid "Analyzes meta title quality including word count, structure, formatting, and clickbait detection for optimal SEO performance."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Attributes/SeoMeta.php:174
msgid "Analyzes multimedia elements (images, videos) in the content for proper optimization, including alt tags, captions, and keyword relevance. Provides suggestions for improving multimedia SEO."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Attributes/SeoMeta.php:175
msgid "Assesses whether page images use modern formats like WebP or AVIF instead of older JPEG or PNG. Reports proportion of legacy files and recommends converting them to enhance load speed and compatibility."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Attributes/SeoMeta.php:176
msgid "Analyzes the opening paragraph of a post for engagement effectiveness. It evaluates the hook strength, emotional appeal, curiosity elements, personal connection with readers, and how well the topic is introduced. This helps ensure that the opening paragraph captures reader interest and sets the stage for the content."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Attributes/SeoMeta.php:177
msgid "Analyzes loading speed metrics and identifies performance bottlenecks to improve user experience and search rankings."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Attributes/SeoMeta.php:178
msgid "Analyzes page load speed using internal metrics and optional external APIs. Generates a performance score and identifies elements slowing the site down, suggesting caching or optimization techniques to achieve faster loading."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Attributes/SeoMeta.php:179
msgid "Evaluates URLs for keyword inclusion, readability, proper length, and hyphen usage to improve search engine visibility."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Attributes/SeoMeta.php:180
msgid "Evaluates keyword frequency, contextual relevance, placement, and content freshness to improve search visibility, and enhance overall user engagement."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Attributes/SeoMeta.php:181
msgid "Analyzes and optimizes website performance and speed to enhance user experience and search engine rankings."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Attributes/SeoMeta.php:182
msgid "Checks if the primary keyword appears in the meta title and ensures it meets word count guidelines. Provides feedback on placement and plugin support to optimize title relevance and user engagement."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Attributes/SeoMeta.php:183
msgid "Analyzes image alt texts for the presence of the primary keyword, ensuring it is used naturally and not excessively. Provides suggestions for optimization based on keyword usage in alt attributes."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Attributes/SeoMeta.php:184
msgid "Evaluates whether the primary keyword appears in the page URL and how close it is to the domain root. Suggests adjustments when keywords are absent or buried deep in the path."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Attributes/SeoMeta.php:185
msgid "Analyzes the meta description to ensure both primary and secondary keywords are included naturally. Provides a ratio of keyword usage and points out missing terms to improve search relevance and keyword diversity."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Attributes/SeoMeta.php:186
msgid "Validates primary and secondary keywords for a post, ensuring they are effectively used in content, titles, headings, and meta descriptions. Analyzes keyword presence, density, and plugin support for SEO optimization."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Attributes/SeoMeta.php:187
msgid "Analyzes content readability and provides suggestions for improvement based on multiple metrics."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Attributes/SeoMeta.php:188
msgid "Analyzes content readability using Flesch-Kincaid scores, sentence complexity, paragraph structure, passive voice usage, and transition word frequency. Provides detailed metrics and suggestions for improving content readability."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Attributes/SeoMeta.php:189
msgid "Analyzes the referring domains of a website to assess backlink quality, diversity, and relevance. Provides insights into the backlink profile including trust flow, citation flow, topical relevance, and geographic distribution."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Attributes/SeoMeta.php:190
msgid "Analyzes the quality of referring links to a page, assessing anchor text distribution, link attributes, and domain ratings"
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Attributes/SeoMeta.php:191
msgid "Checks how supplementary keywords related to the main topic are integrated into the content. Evaluates their placement and frequency to enhance semantic context without overshadowing the primary keyword focus."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Attributes/SeoMeta.php:192
msgid "Validates usage of the srcset attribute so images load appropriate sizes on different devices. Identifies pages with too many non-responsive images and advises implementing responsive techniques to improve performance and mobile SEO."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Attributes/SeoMeta.php:193
msgid "Checks meta robots tags, HTTP headers, and robots.txt to verify that important pages are crawlable while restricting unwanted sections. Highlights misconfigured directives that could prevent indexing."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Attributes/SeoMeta.php:194
msgid "Fetches and analyzes the robots.txt file to confirm correct directives. Ensures important resources are accessible and harmful blocks are removed, providing tips to balance crawler control and SEO."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Attributes/SeoMeta.php:195
msgid "Uses Google`s Safe Browsing API to determine whether a page is flagged for malware or phishing. Reports potential security issues and advises remediation to protect visitors and preserve search engine trust."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Attributes/SeoMeta.php:196
msgid "Analyzes structured data for proper schema usage and guideline adherence to improve indexing, rich results, and search performance."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Attributes/SeoMeta.php:197
msgid "Validates structured data against Google's guidelines to ensure markup is properly implemented. Checks schema types and required fields, reporting errors so search engines can display rich snippets accurately."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Attributes/SeoMeta.php:198
msgid "Analyzes page content to detect existing schema types and recommends appropriate markup when missing. Validates current structured data implementation to ensure compatibility with search engine standards."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Attributes/SeoMeta.php:199
msgid "Evaluates website indexability through search engine presence, robots.txt configuration, meta directives, and security status checks."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Attributes/SeoMeta.php:200
msgid "Reviews meta titles for the presence of recommended secondary keywords. Calculates how many appear and whether they exceed length guidelines, offering suggestions to balance keyword diversity without overcrowding the title."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Attributes/SeoMeta.php:201
msgid "Analyzes and optimizes technical aspects of SEO, including URL structure, canonical tags, schema markup, and search engine indexation."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Attributes/SeoMeta.php:202
msgid "Measures the total length of the page URL and compares it to a recommended threshold. Alerts when URLs become excessively long, offering tips to shorten and simplify paths for better crawling."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Attributes/SeoMeta.php:203
msgid "Evaluates URL structure for clarity and simplicity, detecting excessive parameters, numeric strings, or confusing paths. Guides improvements to create short, readable URLs that clearly describe page content."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Attributes/SeoMeta.php:204
msgid "Evaluates canonical tag implementation, cross-domain references, and duplicate content detection to prevent search engine indexing issues."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:351
msgid "Your meta title contains too many words. Please aim to keep it below 6 words for optimal SEO performance."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:354
msgid "Meta Title Contains Too Many Words"
msgstr ""

