#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:367
#, php-format
msgid "This page has too many headings. For better readability and SEO, use no more than %d headings per 1000 words."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:370
msgid "Reduce Excessive Headings"
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:374
msgid "Your meta title has inconsistent capitalization. Use proper capitalization rules to improve readability and professionalism. Capitalize all words longer than 3 letters, and always capitalize the first and last word of the title."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:377
msgid "Improve Meta Title Capitalization"
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:381
msgid "Transition words connect ideas smoothly. Use them to guide readers through your content logically. Add transition words like \"however,\" \"furthermore,\" or \"consequently\" to improve flow."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:384
msgid "Use more transition words"
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:388
msgid "Your page has very few websites linking to it. Getting links from at least 10 different websites will help search engines trust your site more and improve your rankings."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:391
msgid "Build More Backlinks"
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:395
msgid "You have some websites linking to you, but getting more links (aim for 50+) will significantly boost your search rankings and make your site more authoritative."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:398
msgid "Expand Your Backlink Profile"
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:402
msgid "The websites linking to you are not very trustworthy. Focus on getting links from respected, authoritative websites in your industry instead of low-quality sites."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:405
msgid "Improve Backlink Quality"
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:409
msgid "Your links look artificial to search engines. Focus on earning links naturally from relevant websites that would genuinely reference your content, rather than using manipulative tactics."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:412
msgid "Balance Your Backlink Profile"
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:416
msgid "Many websites linking to you are not related to your industry. Focus on getting links from websites in your specific field, as these are more valuable for SEO."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:419
msgid "Increase Topical Relevance of Backlinks"
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:423
msgid "You do not have links from highly respected websites. Even just a few links from trusted, popular sites can significantly boost your search rankings."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:426
msgid "Acquire High-Authority Backlinks"
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:430
msgid "Your links come from too few types of websites or regions. Getting links from diverse sources looks more natural to search engines and improves rankings."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:433
msgid "Diversify Your Backlink Sources"
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:437
msgid "You are losing more links than you are gaining. This signals declining relevance to search engines. Create a consistent strategy to earn new links regularly."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:440
msgid "Address Declining Backlink Trend"
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:444
msgid "The clickable text in your backlinks is not varied enough. Aim for a natural mix of branded text, keywords, and generic phrases like \"click here\"."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:447
msgid "Improve Anchor Text Distribution"
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:451
msgid "Too many of your backlinks use exact keyword phrases as clickable text. This looks manipulative to search engines. Aim for more natural, varied link text."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:454
msgid "Reduce Over-Optimized Anchor Text"
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:458
msgid "Many of your backlinks use vague text like \"click here\" or \"read more\". These provide less SEO value than descriptive text that includes your brand or keywords."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:461
msgid "Reduce Generic Anchor Text Usage"
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:465
msgid "Some of your backlinks use text that is unrelated to your business or content. Try to get links with text that actually relates to what you offer."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:468
msgid "Address Irrelevant Anchor Text"
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:472
msgid "Not enough links use your brand name as the clickable text. Brand-name links help establish your authority and create a natural-looking link profile."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:475
msgid "Increase Branded Anchor Text"
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:479
msgid "Few of your backlinks use relevant keywords as clickable text. Having some (but not too many) keyword-rich links helps search engines understand your content's topic."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:482
msgid "Add Relevant Keyword Anchors"
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:486
msgid "Too many of your links are marked \"nofollow,\" which limits their SEO value. Focus on getting more standard \"dofollow\" links from reputable websites."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:489
msgid "Balance Nofollow/Dofollow Ratio"
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:493
msgid "Your backlink profile lacks contextual links (links embedded within relevant content). These are more valuable than links in footers, sidebars, or author bios."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:496
msgid "Acquire More Contextual Backlinks"
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:500
msgid "Your selected keywords face intense competition. Pivot toward alternative terms with moderate competition to enhance visibility and achieve better ranking positions."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:503
msgid "Target Lower Competition Keywords"
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:507
msgid "Look for keywords with a good balance between search volume and competition. Ideal keywords have moderate search volume with relatively low competition."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:510
msgid "Balance Search Volume and Competition"
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:514
msgid "Keywords with higher CPC (Cost Per Click) often indicate higher commercial intent. For conversion-focused pages, prioritize keywords with good CPC values."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:517
msgid "Consider Commercial Intent"
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:521
msgid "Your keyword strategy relies on too few terms. Diversify with a blend of competitive and niche keywords to capture broader traffic and achieve sustainable ranking growth."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:524
msgid "Expand Your Keyword Portfolio"
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:528
msgid "Your content omits specific multi-word phrases that attract highly targeted visitors. Incorporate these longer, conversational keyword variations to capture users with precise search intent."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:531
msgid "Target Long Tail Variations"
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:535
msgid "Your site needs a structured keyword mapping strategy. Create a comprehensive plan assigning specific terms to each page, preventing content overlap and maximizing topical authority."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:538
msgid "Create a Keyword Map"
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:542
msgid "You have multiple pages targeting the same keywords, which confuses search engines about which page to rank. Either combine these pages into one stronger page or make each page focus on different keywords to avoid competing with yourself."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:545
msgid "Fix Keyword Cannibalization"
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:549
msgid "Your keyword distribution is uneven. Some topics have too many pages while others have too few. Balance your keyword targeting across content."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:552
#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:713
#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:797
msgid "Improve Keyword Distribution"
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:556
msgid "Your site needs content addressing several industry-relevant keywords. Develop strategic pages targeting these untapped opportunities to capture additional search traffic and audience segments."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:559
msgid "Expand Keyword Coverage"
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:563
msgid "Your website isn't seen as an authority on this topic. Create a main page (pillar page) about your core topic, then link to related pages that cover specific aspects in more detail. This connected structure shows search engines you're an expert on the subject."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:566
msgid "Strengthen Topical Authority"
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:570
msgid "Your content doesn't have a main keyword to target. Choose one specific phrase that best represents what your page is about. This helps search engines understand your content and show it to the right people."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:573
msgid "Set Primary Keyword"
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:577
msgid "Your content focuses too much on just one keyword. Add 2-3 related phrases (secondary keywords) that people might also search for. This helps your page appear in more search results and attract more visitors."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:580
#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:783
msgid "Add Secondary Keywords"
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:584
msgid "Your main keyword isn't placed in the most important parts of your content. Make sure to include it in your title, first paragraph, at least one heading, and meta description. These locations have the biggest impact on search rankings."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:587
msgid "Place Keywords in Strategic Locations"
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:591
msgid "Your main keyword appears either too frequently or not often enough in your content. Try to use it in about 1-2% of your text (1-2 times per 100 words). This makes your content relevant without looking like you're trying to manipulate search rankings."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:594
msgid "Maintain Optimal Keyword Density"
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:598
msgid "Your main keyword isn't being used effectively throughout your content. Make sure to include it naturally in important places like your title, headings, and throughout your text. This helps search engines understand what your page is about."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:601
msgid "Optimize Primary Keyword Usage"
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:605
msgid "Your content contains excessive keyword repetition. Diversify your language with synonyms and related terms to maintain natural flow while preserving search relevance."
msgstr ""

#: app/src/Domain/Integrations/WordPress/Seo/Entities/Optimiser/Base/Enums/Suggestion.php:608
